      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="如何成為pixiv會員？" class="article-title">
          如何成為pixiv會員？
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>按下pixiv首頁的「<a href="https://accounts.pixiv.net/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener">立即註冊</a>」完成註冊手續即可成為pixiv會員。</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

